</li>
<li>
<p>9 Mar, London, <a href="http://www.insidegovernment.co.uk/event-details/enhancing-research-collaboration/642">The Dowling Review: Enhancing Business-University Research Collaboration</a>.&nbsp; [Inside Government]</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>10 Mar, London, <a href="http://www.hefce.ac.uk/news/Events/Name,104683,en.html">Next steps for policy on widening participation and the changing shape of HE admissions</a>.&nbsp; [HEA]</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>15 Mar, Salford, <a href="http://www.salford.ac.uk/onecpd/courses/the-future-of-further-education-and-higher-education">The Future of Further Education and Higher Education</a>.&nbsp; [University of Salford]</p>
