                    <item>
              <title>e-Learning Digest No 134 - Oct 15</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/9399</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/9399</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>UK </strong><strong>Conferences &amp; Workshops&nbsp;</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>3 Nov, London, <a href="http://www.westminsterforumprojects.co.uk/forums/event.php?eid=1066">Building better research relationships between industry and academia</a>.&nbsp; [Westminster Forum]</p>
