<p>~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</p>
<p><strong>e-Learning MOOCs</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>15 Aug&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (5 wks)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="https://openeducation.blackboard.com/mooc-catalog/courseDetails/view?course_id=_458_1">Adventures in Self-Blended Learning</a>, Concordia University (Blackboard)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>17 Aug&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (5 wks x 3 hrs)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="https://www.coursera.org/course/k12virtualtrends?siteID=.GqSdLGGurk-qO3c7_SUJ3Hh8mrGE6oo.A&utm_medium=partners&utm_source=linkshare&utm_campaign=*GqSdLGGurk&utm_content=10">Emerging Trends &amp; Technologies in the Virtual K-12 Classroom</a>, University of California (Coursera)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>24 Aug&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (2 wks x 3 hrs)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/online-learning">Get Started with Online Learning</a>, OU (FutureLearn)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>31 Aug&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (5 wks x 4 hrs)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="https://www.coursera.org/course/digitalstorytelling">Powerful Tools for Teaching and Learning: Digital Storytelling</a>, University of Houston (Coursera)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>16 Sep&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (11 wks)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="https://www.edx.org/course/social-learning-social-impact-mcgillx-groocx">Social Learning for Social Impact</a>, McGill (edX)</p>
</li>
