</li>
<li>
<p>Dyson is investing $15m in a <a href="http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/mar/16/dyson-invests-15m-in-technology-that-may-double-smartphone-battery-life">new type of solid state battery</a> that promises to double battery life for smartphones and electric cars.&nbsp; [The Guardian]</p>
</li>
