<p>&hellip;and an overview of <a href="http://www.pewinternet.org/2015/04/09/teens-social-media-technology-2015/">Teens, Social Media &amp; Technology</a> (showing that 24% are online &ldquo;almost constantly&rdquo;).&nbsp; [Audrey Watters]</p>
