<li>
<p>Interesting eleven-page <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/edit?id=1TQupkuKAo7HQT-Sc8wMOcqVvXtc9j4QGWA2BrfBWpbI&hl=en">A-Z list of Google tools and projects</a>, from Aardvark through to Zeitgeist.&nbsp; [Stephen Downes]</p>
