<p>Apple is going to allow educational system admins to <a href="http://www.theverge.com/2015/3/8/8170205/apple-will-make-it-easier-for-schools-to-use-ipads-by-dropping-apple">download apps and content to shared iPads</a> without requiring an Apple ID.&nbsp; [The Verge]</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>The <a href="http://thenextweb.com/google/2015/03/12/googles-art-project-chrome-extension-brings-classic-paintings-to-every-new-tab/">Google Art Project</a> puts a fine art image on every new Chrome tab you open.&nbsp; [TNW]</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="http://venturebeat.com/2015/02/15/helpouts-r-i-p-googles-build-it-and-they-will-come-approach-ultimately-failed-health-practitioners/">Google is closing its Helpouts platform</a> which enabled experts to offer advice via video chat.&nbsp; [VentureBeat]</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Point your phone camera at an equation and <a href="http://techcrunch.com/2015/02/27/photomath-brings-its-awesome-math-equation-solving-app-to-android/">PhotoMath</a> will give you the answer and show you all the steps required.&nbsp; [TechCrunch]</p>
</li>
