              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/8792</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/8792</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>UK </strong><strong>Conferences &amp; Workshops</strong><strong style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->&nbsp;</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>30 Sep-1 Oct, Birmingham, <a href="https://www.learnevents.com/index.php">22<sup>nd</sup> World of Learning Conference &amp; Exhibition</a>.&nbsp; [LearnEvents]</li>
<li>9 Oct, Manchester, <a href="http://www.salford.ac.uk/spd/coursedetails?courseid=HIGHERuWIk&utm_medium=email&utm_source=Salford+Professional+Development+Ltd&utm_campaign=3865558_Copy+of+Leading+Through+Change:+Higher+Education+(6)&dm_i=21L7,2AUOM,ES51KL,8CC2O,1">Leading through Change: Higher Education Leadership Programme</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</li>
<li>15 Oct, London, <a href="http://www.skillcast.com/web/the_new_experience">Compliance e-Learning: The New Experience</a>.&nbsp; [Skillcast]</li>
