<li>5 Mar, Nottingham, <a href="http://www.heacademy.ac.uk/events/detail/2014/Seminars/Themes/GEN967_nottingham">Online and open: modelling sustainability and 'greening the academy' through e-learning</a>.&nbsp; [HEA]</li>
