<li>19 Mar, Cardiff, <a href="http://www.heacademy.ac.uk/events/detail/2014/NTT_OpenAccess_Cardiff">New to using open access resources in teaching research methods</a>.&nbsp; [HEA]</li>
<li>20 Mar, Online, <a href="http://engage.vevent.com/index.jsp?eid=630&seid=2330">Enterprise Learning! Virtual Summit</a>.&nbsp; [Elearning!]</li>
<li>21 Mar, Cardiff, <a href="http://www.heacademy.ac.uk/events/detail/2014/Seminars/AH/GEN908_Cardiff_University">Utilizing Digital technology and social media in language classes</a>.&nbsp; [HEA]</li>
