<ul>
<li>Microsoft is making <a href="http://campustechnology.com/articles/2013/10/17/microsoft-to-make-office-365-proplus-free-for-students.aspx">Office 365 ProPlus</a> (which includes desktop applications) free for some students from Dec.&nbsp; [Campus Technology]</li>
<li>iPhoneza reveals <a href="http://mashable.com/2013/10/02/ios-7-hidden-features/">8 hidden features in iOS 7</a>.&nbsp; And then <a href="http://iphoneza.co.za/8-more-hidden-ios-7-features/">another eight</a>.&nbsp; [iPhoneza]</li>
<li>Richard Byrne lists <a href="http://ipadapps4school.com/2013/10/17/seven-free-science-apps-for-ipads/">Seven Free Science Apps for iPads</a>.&nbsp; [iPad Apps For School]</li>
