                    <item>
              <title>George: My dream: Redesign &amp; run First Steps into Learning and Teaching MOOC</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6821</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6821</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>I have written this using the "OPEN" framework: Outcomes, Present stiuation, Exploration of alternatives, Next steps</p>
<h3>Outcomes</h3>
<ul>
<li>Achieve accreditation for one (or more?) (open?) online courses on topics about teaching in higher education, within the framework of the Brookes (OCSLD) New Lecturers Programme</li>
<li>Exceed 200 participants satisfied, engaged, active and enjoying the open&nbsp; online course, "First steps into learning and teaching in higher education"</li>
<li>Achieve 25 (fee-paying) enrolments for assessment and CATS credit (pending, see above) on the open online course</li>
<li>Complete revision of the design for "First Steps into Learning and Teaching in Higher Education (fslt) 2013" (massive) open online course.</li>
<li>Develop other courses within the framework?</li>
</ul>
<h3>Present Situation</h3>
<ul>
<li>National and institutional developments in open online courses...</li>
<li>Successful pilot of fslt last year (http://openbrookes.net/firststeps12/)</li>
<li>Successful programme of closed, non-accredited on-line courses</li>
<li>Respected, successful HEA accredited PG Cert</li>
</ul>
<h3>Explore (Alternatives)</h3>
<ul>
<li>MOOC with accreditation</li>
<li>Non-accredited MOOC</li>
<li>Accredited closed course?</li>
<li>Non-accredited (cpd) closed course</li>
<li>Do nothing? (Not an option?)</li>
<li>What else?</li>
</ul>
<h3>Next steps</h3>
<ul>
<li>Form study circle in OLDS MOOC in parallel with programme development group (PDG)</li>
<li>Set up Google doc for collaborative working</li>
<li>Set deadlines</li>
</ul>]]></description>
